{"tid":1104782,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"同親家姐打茄輪原來係有可能","createTime":"2019-04-13T11:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T14:56:05.000Z","uid":57898,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"feaeaff7b79c5aa6233a9146fdac964249e63db1","tid":1104782,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:18:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q9R3hAJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9R3hAJ.png&h=c0871581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國一位名為 Chris Monroe 的男網紅，為了獲得更高的影片點閱率，竟說服親姐姐和自己「打茄輪」，挑戰不倫SOD &hellip;Chris 先是在社群網站上PO 出和同父異母姐姐 Kaitlyn O&rsquo;Connor 的合照，接著他在貼文中寫下，「如果這張照片超過三萬讚，我就錄一段和姐姐「打茄輪」的影片。」網友們大多以為是開玩笑，所以紛紛按讚，讚數果然很快就超過三萬。<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，Chris 果真找姐姐 Kaitlyn 來拍影片，在影片一開始，Kaitlyn 有先表明不太願意接受 Chris 的要求，但最後還是被 Chris 說服了，兩人真的在鏡頭前忘情舌吻，還深情地閉上眼睛，雖然 Kaitlyn 仍多次害羞地說不想再做同樣的事情，而Chris也顯得臉紅 &hellip;<br />\n<br />\n這支影片至今已累積超過350萬的點閱率，網友們一面倒痛批，「這是不倫！」「好噁心！」「我看得好尷尬！」「思想扭曲！」有網友表示，Chris 和 Kaitlyn 的行為已經違法。<br />\n<br />\n也有眼尖的網友發現，影片4分06秒處，鏡頭外 Chris 的另一隻手疑似在摸姐姐的下半身。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ndS6fnh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FndS6fnh.png&h=61434a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然招來大量的批評聲浪，但 Chris 沒有再對此發表任何看法，也沒有把影片下架。網路捧紅很多人，但藉由今天的例子，我們不禁想問，為了獲得高點閱率，人們的價值觀是否因此扭曲？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HfDnUpXpKTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHfDnUpXpKTM&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhA9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=f35f5bd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HfDnUpXpKTM</a>"},{"pid":"8afe2a3d9e7a4fa2397eb32203e44740c951f442","tid":1104782,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"個女似感覺麻麻 但個男似覺得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7806230f5b4e301adaa87948557b91230d22db","tid":1104782,"uid":57898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8afe2a3d9e7a4fa2397eb32203e44740c951f442","tid":1104782,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:25:49.000Z","msg":"個女似感覺麻麻 但個男似覺得舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:26:36.000Z","msg":"個男其實紅都面曬"},{"pid":"9058893b72180ad08ff60382d3719ee106088f05","tid":1104782,"uid":82917,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"真係好核突睇到想嘔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申有家姐"},{"pid":"cdcb14fd97eaeef73be0f2a628ea0197f809106d","tid":1104782,"uid":237024,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:31:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"405a13b43e46c91dcd52cf4d8dce9936fb04f233","tid":1104782,"uid":24737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"波仔同佢家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c700259ded52ce346f3abe4744843362aa8b72a","tid":1104782,"uid":173659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:33:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e088a6c1db56457212515c95e3a6cb2676a0bc01","tid":1104782,"uid":49456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:34:04.000Z","msg":"一定有屌"},{"pid":"1d56de4a1af2ea53464bc852886eecb7035d2528","tid":1104782,"uid":171594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"405a13b43e46c91dcd52cf4d8dce9936fb04f233","tid":1104782,"uid":24737,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"波仔同佢家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:35:36.000Z","msg":"兩個都咁醜樣<br />\n佢兩個扑野都唔想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a0127eb10d36ba68b1812842d7d8522005e6bfa","tid":1104782,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T11:36:48.00